    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and making sure every inch stays sparkling. If you're looking for total perfection and a ride that's been truly loved, this is the one! I'd love to tell you more about it, so feel free to reach out and say hi!",
      "price": 43500.0,
